items.name: qubes-os-fix-refresh-rate-bash-script
items.description: Automates screen resolution and refresh rate setup in Qubes OS. The script prompts for resolution and refresh rate, validates inputs, generates a configuration file, and adds it to autostart. It automatically applies settings on system startup using xrandr. Works with virtual screen DUMMY0.
